msgstr "Berhasil keluar"

msgid "Goodbye, %1. See you next time!"
msgstr "Selamat tinggal, %1. Sampai jumpa!"

msgid "Your session has been securely closed."
msgstr "Sesi Anda telah ditutup dengan aman."

msgid "Redirecting to login in %1 seconds."
msgstr "Mengalihkan ke halaman login dalam %1 detik."

msgid "Securely logged out"
msgstr "Berhasil keluar dengan aman"

msgid "All session data has been securely deleted from this device."
msgstr "Semua data sesi telah dihapus dengan aman dari perangkat ini."

msgid "Email still active"
msgstr "Email masih aktif"

msgid "New tickets can be submitted at any time by sending an email."
msgstr "Tiket baru dapat dikirimkan kapan saja melalui email."

msgid "Your tickets are safe"
msgstr "Tiket Anda aman"

msgid "Your open tickets remain saved and continue to be processed."
msgstr "Tiket terbuka Anda tetap tersimpan dan terus diproses."

msgid "Want to sign in again?"
msgstr "Ingin masuk lagi?"


